io.s4.zeno.config
Interface ConfigMap

All Known Subinterfaces:
WritableConfigMap
All Known Implementing Classes:
JSONConfigMap, RootedConfigMap, RootedWritableConfigMap, ZKConfigMap, ZKWritableConfigMap
public interface ConfigMap

A key-value map. The keys are strings. The values may be interpreted as a variety of types: see the getters for all options. It is recommended that the keys be structured hierarchically with dots (.) as separators, like java package names. This allows the creation of maps with a subspace of keys.
